OL,3,CSEND students told to find their own
OL,4,Cway to college as council axes
OL,5,Ctransport
OL,7,FSchoolmates Mia Veichmanis and Alfie
OL,8,FFurnival were due to start at a
OL,9,Fspecialist college in September 2025,
OL,10,Fbut those plans are now on hold after
OL,11,FBury Council announced it is axing its
OL,12,Fdoor-to-door transport for disabled
OL,13,Fstudents over the age of 16.
OL,15,FThe teenagers both have a host of
OL,16,Fhealth issues and complex needs and
OL,17,Fare unable to get to the college on
OL,18,Fpublic transport.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/14
