OL,4,Cway to college as council axes
OL,5,Ctransport
OL,7,FBury Council currently provide a
OL,8,Fspecial bus service to take them to
OL,9,Fand from school but that service will
OL,10,Fstop when they go to college.
OL,12,FThe families say the door-to-door
OL,13,Ftransport is vital as there is no
OL,14,Fother way they can get their children
OL,15,Fto college unless they give up their
OL,16,Fjobs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/14
