OL,7,FThe families say school is somewhere
OL,8,Ftheir children can be themselves and
OL,9,Fbe with their friends.
OL,11,F"She just absolutely loves it," Lynne
OL,12,Fsaid. "She loves being with her
OL,13,Ffriends, she loves people interacting
OL,14,Fwith her, doing different stuff every
OL,15,Fday, it's so nice to see the pictures
OL,16,Fwhen she's so happy."
OL,18,FNatalie added: "Every day it's 'is it
OL,19,Fschool tomorrow, is it school
OL,20,Ftomorrow?' He loves it.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/14
