OL,7,F"Whereas at home there's not much to
OL,8,Fdo, he's not allowed out the garden
OL,9,Fgate, he just loves all the stuff in
OL,10,Fschool."
OL,12,FThe families have started a petition
OL,13,Fas part of a campaign against the
OL,14,Fchanges.
OL,16,FBury Council has declared itself to be
OL,17,Fin "a state of financial distress" and
OL,18,Fis facing a #22 million gap in its
OL,19,Fbudget for the next year.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/14
