OL,7,FThe council said with soaring costs
OL,8,Fthey have been left with no choice but
OL,9,Fto remove a service they are not
OL,10,Flegally obliged to provide.
OL,12,FIn a statement provided to ITV Granada
OL,13,FReports, Bury Council said: "Our home-
OL,14,Fto-school transport policy was changed
OL,15,Fin June to bring it into line with
OL,16,FGovernment guidelines.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/14
