OL,7,F"There is no legal duty on a local
OL,8,Fauthority to provide free or
OL,9,Fsubsidised transport for those
OL,10,Fattending post-16 education. However,
OL,11,Fwe recognise that many families and
OL,12,Fstudents with SEND would experience
OL,13,Fdifficulty accessing post-16 provision.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
