OL,3,CSEND students told to find their own
OL,4,Cway to college as council axes
OL,5,Ctransport
OL,7,F"Families who were already receiving
OL,8,Ftravel assistance under the old policy
OL,9,Fwill have those arrangements protected
OL,10,Funtil a change in their circumstances
OL,11,For following a review of their child's
OL,12,FEHC Plan. All Year 11 students have to
OL,13,Freapply for travel assistance when
OL,14,Ftransferring to post-16 education.
OL,16,F"The new policy was developed
OL,17,Ffollowing extensive consultation with
OL,18,Ffamilies and representative groups,
OL,19,Fand a full equality impact assessment
OL,20,Fto identify those who would be
OL,21,Faffected by the change in policy.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/14
