OL,5,Ctransport
OL,7,F"In Bury we are doing our best to do
OL,8,Fboth. Even in this climate of soaring
OL,9,Fcosts and a huge rise in demand for
OL,10,FSEND services, we always strive to put
OL,11,Fthe child at the heart of what we do
OL,12,Fand meet their needs accordingly.
OL,14,F"Processes are not always perfect, and
OL,15,Fwe would encourage residents to
OL,16,Fcontinue to engage with us."
